


How NG implementing 2-way data-binding ?


NG life-cycle ,   on bootstrap

phase-1 : compilation

on every DOM elememnt which having directive(s)/expressions , 
where angular will register 'watch expressions' / listeners


watch-expressions  will read/write model data when becomes dirty.


all watch-expressions are executed by 'digest-loop' given NG-framework.


--------------------------

we can also register  custom watchers

-----------------------------